Mothercare Investor Says Pay Plan ‘Highly Excessive,’ FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-05T00:24:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-05/mothercare-investor-says-pay-plan-highly-excessive-ft-reports.html
Mothercare Plc (MTC)  shareholder, VGI
Partners, said the company’s executive incentive plan is
“highly excessive” and demanded that it be “immediately
reviewed,’” the Financial Times reported, citing a July 4
letter to the chairman of Mothercare’s board from Sydney,
Australia-based VGI, which holds 1 percent of the retailer’s
stock.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
